21
00:02:09,000 --> 00:02:10,930
We are just missing your dolls now.

22
00:02:13,150 --> 00:02:14,080
But the thing is,

23
00:02:15,190 --> 00:02:16,450
when are you moving in?

24
00:02:19,800 --> 00:02:20,360
Anytime.

25
00:02:25,000 --> 00:02:27,150
As Tang Yu's fiancée,

26
00:02:28,030 --> 00:02:29,829
I moved into the Tangs' mansion.

27
00:02:30,800 --> 00:02:33,260
And that was the beginning
of my misfortune.

28
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:35,200
What happened later?

29
00:02:36,680 --> 00:02:37,560
This family

30
00:02:38,440 --> 00:02:40,070
