Our parents died early.

56
00:04:53,190 --> 00:04:54,720
We didn't know anything...

57
00:04:55,180 --> 00:04:55,920
We only knew that

58
00:04:55,920 --> 00:04:57,480
we were the closest people to each other.

59
00:04:57,480 --> 00:04:58,810
But it's different now.

60
00:04:59,240 --> 00:05:00,100
Now we have you.

61
00:05:00,800 --> 00:05:02,400
My brother really likes you.

62
00:05:03,730 --> 00:05:04,720
Do you even

63
