hear yourself?

64
00:05:06,000 --> 00:05:06,950
You are insane.

65
00:05:07,160 --> 00:05:08,030
You and your brother

66
00:05:08,030 --> 00:05:08,960
are both insane!

67
00:05:09,190 --> 00:05:11,050
I am leaving this house right now.

68
00:05:11,190 --> 00:05:12,000
You two,

69
00:05:12,310 --> 00:05:13,430
