70
00:05:17,560 --> 00:05:18,090
Brother.

71
00:05:24,430 --> 00:05:25,360
Get out of the way.

72
00:05:25,360 --> 00:05:26,830
How could you push my sister?

73
00:05:26,830 --> 00:05:28,490
I told you to get out of the way!

74
00:05:31,270 --> 00:05:32,110
How dare you?

75
00:06:06,480 --> 00:06:07,280
Open the door.

76
00:06:07,600 --> 00:06:08,400
Open the door.

77
00:06:09,920 --> 00:06:10,830
Let me out.

78
00:06:40,480 --> 00:06:41,340
How much longer

79
00:06:43,159 --> 00:06:44,750
are you going to lock me up?

80
00:06:50,480 --> 00:06:51,630
What you are doing is

81
