90
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:11,950
So,

91
00:08:12,750 --> 00:08:13,560
you've been trapped

92
00:08:13,560 --> 00:08:14,760
in that strange body?

93
00:08:14,950 --> 00:08:16,480
