96
00:08:19,750 --> 00:08:21,360
I can only be trapped there.

97
00:08:22,740 --> 00:08:24,180
How does the saying go?

98
00:08:25,560 --> 00:08:27,430
You can run, but you can't hide.

99
00:08:28,040 --> 00:08:29,700
Their ancestral home is here,

100
00:08:30,420 --> 00:08:30,980
so

101
