They didn't do anything to you.

114
00:08:49,510 --> 00:08:50,910
The son pays for the father's sins!

115
00:08:50,910 --> 00:08:53,040
Their ancestors committed the crime.

116
00:08:53,860 --> 00:08:54,840
What's wrong with me

117
00:08:54,840 --> 00:08:56,100
