122
00:09:04,080 --> 00:09:05,000
You mean...

123
00:09:07,240 --> 00:09:08,720
What you're saying is none of my concern.

124
00:09:08,720 --> 00:09:10,120
They didn't hurt anyone.

125
00:09:10,150 --> 00:09:11,270
But I was paid to solve

126
00:09:11,270 --> 00:09:12,030
