135
00:09:26,750 --> 00:09:28,840
I-I used to be a perfectly normal person.

136
00:09:28,840 --> 00:09:30,320
I didn't want to be a demon!

137
00:09:30,360 --> 00:09:30,840
Master,

138
00:09:30,910 --> 00:09:32,240
I was wrong. I was wrong.

139
00:09:32,550 --> 00:09:33,880
Demon, no more excuses.

140
00:09:33,910 --> 00:09:34,570
Fire, come!

141
00:09:39,120 --> 00:09:39,750
Wait!

142
00:09:42,600 --> 00:09:44,390
She didn't become a demon voluntarily.

143
00:09:44,390 --> 00:09:45,580
Is there any way

144
00:09:45,790 --> 00:09:47,480
to free her

145
00:09:47,510 --> 00:09:48,570
from that dog skin?

146
00:09:49,260 --> 00:09:51,080
She has already turned
into a pile of dry bones.

147
00:09:51,080 --> 00:09:51,840
After 100 years,

148
00:09:51,840 --> 00:09:52,340
she is now

149
00:09:52,340 --> 00:09:53,810
an utterly great demon.

150
00:09:53,840 --> 00:09:54,530
There's no cure for her,

151
00:09:54,530 --> 00:09:56,390
and her hatred is extremely deep.

152
00:09:57,080 --> 00:09:58,480
Didn't she already admit

153
00:09:58,510 --> 00:09:59,870
that she was wrong?

154
00:10:00,080 --> 00:10:01,240
Wait, you trust a demon

155
00:10:01,240 --> 00:10:02,110
