166
00:10:16,390 --> 00:10:18,050
Just give her one last chance!

167
00:10:18,320 --> 00:10:19,050
I have a plan.

168
00:10:19,720 --> 00:10:20,320
What is it?

169
00:10:20,670 --> 00:10:22,270
To be honest with each other.

170
00:10:29,000 --> 00:10:29,630
Really?

171
00:10:30,670 --> 00:10:31,400
Can you do it?

172
00:10:33,440 --> 00:10:36,390
Letting the dog live on the second floor

173
00:10:36,600 --> 00:10:38,030
is a bit weird,

174
00:10:38,510 --> 00:10:39,510
but that room is

175
00:10:39,960 --> 00:10:41,510
empty anyway.

176
00:10:41,790 --> 00:10:43,150
Y-Yes, we can do it.

177
00:10:45,750 --> 00:10:46,510
Actually,

178
00:10:47,120 --> 00:10:48,720
you just need to act as usual.

179
00:10:48,870 --> 00:10:49,840
Don't be afraid.

180
00:10:50,720 --> 00:10:51,920
Just treat her as a dog

181
00:10:52,910 --> 00:10:54,150
