187
00:11:03,630 --> 00:11:05,200
You call this
being honest with each other?

188
00:11:05,200 --> 00:11:05,670
Sort of.

189
00:11:05,980 --> 00:11:06,930
Sort of? You...

190
00:11:06,960 --> 00:11:07,690
You completely made up

191
00:11:07,690 --> 00:11:08,670
a whole different story.

192
00:11:08,670 --> 00:11:09,800
It's not bad, right?

193
00:11:10,120 --> 00:11:11,630
The brother of the siblings
from a century ago

194
00:11:11,630 --> 00:11:12,910
had an affair with the maid,

195
00:11:12,910 --> 00:11:14,980
who was accidentally killed by the sister.

196
00:11:14,980 --> 00:11:16,200
The maid had her resentment

197
00:11:16,200 --> 00:11:17,240
attached to a dog

198
00:11:17,480 --> 00:11:18,540
and became a demon.

199
00:11:19,440 --> 00:11:21,100
The truth is a bit complicated

200
00:11:21,320 --> 00:11:21,920
and scary.

201
00:11:22,790 --> 00:11:24,360
I was afraid they couldn't accept it

202
00:11:24,360 --> 00:11:25,020
right away.

203
00:11:25,480 --> 00:11:26,670
If the brother and sister

204
00:11:26,670 --> 00:11:28,030
treat He Feng well

205
00:11:28,270 --> 00:11:29,870
and save her from wandering,

206
00:11:29,870 --> 00:11:30,470
any hatred

207
00:11:30,750 --> 00:11:31,840
should fade away.

208
00:11:32,390 --> 00:11:33,850
I think this is the only way

209
00:11:34,160 --> 00:11:34,970
to avoid

210
00:11:35,000 --> 00:11:36,530
