211
00:11:37,320 --> 00:11:38,780
This is also a last resort.

212
00:11:39,150 --> 00:11:40,630
She's already such a poor thing.

213
00:11:40,630 --> 00:11:41,240
Are you really

214
00:11:41,240 --> 00:11:42,150
going to burn her

215
00:11:42,150 --> 00:11:42,960
