216
00:11:44,150 --> 00:11:44,530
Wait...

217
00:11:44,530 --> 00:11:45,100
Sirs.

218
00:11:48,480 --> 00:11:50,010
I still can't rest assured.

219
00:11:50,040 --> 00:11:50,900
Now that we know

220
00:11:50,910 --> 00:11:51,970
