236
00:12:15,960 --> 00:12:17,160
Let's drop it for now.

237
00:12:21,200 --> 00:12:21,800
Fang Yuan!

238
00:12:23,440 --> 00:12:23,870
Lin!

239
00:12:34,480 --> 00:12:35,610
These two gentlemen

240
00:12:35,790 --> 00:12:37,050
