245
00:12:46,600 --> 00:12:47,200
Fang Yuan.

246
00:12:48,030 --> 00:12:49,000
Boyfriend?

247
00:12:49,440 --> 00:12:51,040
Why so distant from me today?

248
00:12:51,790 --> 00:12:52,670
I am

249
00:12:53,320 --> 00:12:54,050
