250
00:12:55,440 --> 00:12:56,240
You are right.

251
00:13:06,550 --> 00:13:07,080
Morning.

252
00:13:08,440 --> 00:13:09,170
Your coffee.

253
00:13:22,840 --> 00:13:23,840
You came so early.

254
00:13:25,150 --> 00:13:26,480
What were you doing yesterday?

255
00:13:26,480 --> 00:13:27,880
Looking up information.

256
00:13:27,910 --> 00:13:28,970
What information?

257
00:13:30,390 --> 00:13:32,200
The information from a century ago.

258
00:13:32,200 --> 00:13:32,860
It was paid,

259
00:13:33,120 --> 00:13:34,320
and quite expensive.

260
00:13:34,710 --> 00:13:37,700
[Republic of China Daily]

261
