271
00:13:53,000 --> 00:13:54,070
These siblings are

272
00:13:54,480 --> 00:13:55,480
also disgusting,

273
00:13:56,080 --> 00:13:58,340
just as disgusting as the ones back then!

274
00:13:59,230 --> 00:14:00,360
If they were really

275
00:14:00,360 --> 00:14:01,820
in a secret relationship,

276
00:14:01,880 --> 00:14:02,790
why would Tang Lin

277
00:14:02,790 --> 00:14:03,750
have a fiancé?

278
00:14:04,390 --> 00:14:05,250
These siblings

279
00:14:06,550 --> 00:14:08,350
have a large ancestral mansion.

280
00:14:08,600 --> 00:14:11,130
They have family property
and plenty of money

281
00:14:11,320 --> 00:14:12,730
and don't need to assimilate
into society at all.

282
00:14:12,730 --> 00:14:14,000
All they need to do is live

283
00:14:14,000 --> 00:14:15,550
their happy lives in their own place.

284
00:14:15,550 --> 00:14:16,350
Wait a minute.

285
00:14:16,360 --> 00:14:17,360
By the same token,

286
00:14:18,120 --> 00:14:19,150
things were exactly the same

287
00:14:19,150 --> 00:14:20,360
for the siblings back then.

288
00:14:20,360 --> 00:14:21,020
Therefore,

289
00:14:21,150 --> 00:14:22,670
these two pairs of siblings

290
00:14:22,670 --> 00:14:24,120
never had any kind

291
00:14:24,270 --> 00:14:25,790
of improper relationship.

292
00:14:25,790 --> 00:14:27,000
He Feng was lying?

293
00:14:27,840 --> 00:14:28,770
She deceived us!

294
00:14:28,870 --> 00:14:29,750
That's why I told you

295
00:14:29,750 --> 00:14:30,910
