296
00:14:30,910 --> 00:14:31,270
But...

297
00:14:31,270 --> 00:14:32,000
No buts.

298
00:14:32,510 --> 00:14:34,150
There are lots of loopholes in her story.

299
00:14:34,150 --> 00:14:34,960
If Tang Huan

300
00:14:34,960 --> 00:14:36,240
had turned her into a dog,

301
00:14:36,240 --> 00:14:38,120
the person she hates the most
should have been

302
00:14:38,120 --> 00:14:39,870
Tang Lin,
who looks identical to Tang Huan.

303
00:14:39,870 --> 00:14:41,320
Why did she try to kill Tang De?

304
00:14:41,320 --> 00:14:42,550
Maybe that was

305
00:14:42,670 --> 00:14:44,670
because Tang De got in the car first.

306
00:14:48,200 --> 00:14:49,460
Open it and take a look.

307
00:14:53,440 --> 00:14:55,670
Is there anything wrong about this photo?

308
00:14:55,670 --> 00:14:57,000
This is He Feng's necklace.

309
00:14:57,000 --> 00:14:58,660
Yes, it is He Feng's necklace.

310
00:14:59,630 --> 00:15:01,390
Tang Yu was her fiancé.

311
00:15:01,890 --> 00:15:02,720
But it was the photo

312
00:15:02,720 --> 00:15:03,980
of Tang Huan inside the necklace

313
00:15:03,980 --> 00:15:04,790
she wore.

314
00:15:05,030 --> 00:15:05,870
Why?

315
00:15:11,790 --> 00:15:13,510
Did your brain stop working
after hearing this?

316
00:15:13,510 --> 00:15:15,360
Mine stopped working after I said it, too.

317
00:15:15,360 --> 00:15:16,870
We need to go back and take a look.

318
00:15:16,870 --> 00:15:18,670
You mean, Fenghua Photo Studio?

319
00:15:27,150 --> 00:15:28,410
What are we doing here?

320
00:15:28,910 --> 00:15:30,240
Looking for something.

321
00:15:30,390 --> 00:15:31,390
Looking for what?

322
00:15:32,390 --> 00:15:32,990
Evidence.

323
00:16:03,080 --> 00:16:03,680
Dongqing.

324
00:16:08,110 --> 00:16:08,630
Found it.

